commit.message:
cp-tree.h (THROW_NAME, [...]): Remove.

	* cp-tree.h (THROW_NAME, AUTO_VTABLE_NAME, AUTO_TEMP_FORMAT,
	VTABLE_BASE, VTABLE_NAME_PREFIX, STATIC_NAME_FORMAT): Remove.

From-SVN: r98504

+	* cp-tree.h (THROW_NAME, AUTO_VTABLE_NAME, AUTO_TEMP_FORMAT,
+	VTABLE_BASE, VTABLE_NAME_PREFIX, STATIC_NAME_FORMAT): Remove.

 	* cp-tree.h: Adjust for new VEC API.
